channel.title: Ancient Battle Axe
channel.description:
Yeah no to steal .....'s thunder, but i thought i would make my own ancient battle axe because i was so moved by his (hahaha right.....) im not saying his is bad, im just saying i made my own... [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/2rc1r9y.jpg[/img]
I kept it really simple because i mean, to be honest, nothing has to look super good in runescape unless its being added to a 562+ (IMO). its not like anything has to look good for a 317 :P [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/iml6yv.jpg[/img]
sorry for the wireframe.. i forgot to turn off faces :P
